1
00:00:19,880 --> 00:00:20,880
There's writing on it

2
00:00:20,880 --> 00:00:21,680
That's right

3
00:00:23,440 --> 00:00:24,480
The Confluence of Nine Rivers

4
00:00:24,880 --> 00:00:25,880
Guarding Chentang

5
00:00:27,120 --> 00:00:28,240
Sincerely praying for prosperity

6
00:00:28,240 --> 00:00:29,280
Favorable winds and rain

7
00:00:30,680 --> 00:00:32,120
Caught you

8
00:00:48,840 --> 00:00:50,320
What in the world is this?

9
00:00:57,200 --> 00:00:58,040
Er Tiao

10
00:00:58,040 --> 00:00:58,880
Get back here

11
00:00:59,800 --> 00:01:00,560
Li Jing

12
00:01:00,560 --> 00:01:01,720
What are you waiting for? Go!

13
00:01:02,360 --> 00:01:03,160
What about her?

14
00:01:04,280 --> 00:01:05,320
She has no magic power left

15
00:01:05,320 --> 00:01:06,200
I can handle this myself

16
00:01:07,600 --> 00:01:08,440
Go, quickly

17
00:01:10,240 --> 00:01:10,960
Be careful

18
00:01:40,280 --> 00:01:40,960
Quick

19
00:01:40,960 --> 00:01:42,080
Open the passage

20
00:01:42,320 --> 00:01:43,600
Or I'll kill you

21
00:01:44,600 --> 00:01:45,520
You think you can?

22
00:01:46,280 --> 00:01:47,800
Do you still have the power to kill me?

23
00:01:52,040 --> 00:01:54,320
Let me go back

24
00:01:54,600 --> 00:01:55,800
You want to go back that badly?

25
00:01:56,560 --> 00:01:57,560
If he doesn't see me

26
00:01:58,160 --> 00:02:00,520
The Ninth Prince will kill all my people

27
00:02:00,520 --> 00:02:01,440
What exactly is going on?

28
00:02:02,160 --> 00:02:04,080
I was originally just an ordinary Clam

29
00:02:04,920 --> 00:02:05,920
When I was young

30
00:02:06,320 --> 00:02:09,120
I accidentally awakened my clan's rare Dream-weaving Power

31
00:02:11,000 --> 00:02:12,480
After the Ninth Prince heard about it

32
00:02:12,920 --> 00:02:14,320
He sent people to take me away

33
00:02:15,680 --> 00:02:17,400
Threatening me with my people

34
00:02:18,480 --> 00:02:20,560
Forcing me to stay by his side and work

35
00:02:22,480 --> 00:02:24,480
Weaving sweet dreams for him every day

36
00:02:27,280 --> 00:02:28,320
If he can't find me

37
00:02:28,680 --> 00:02:30,160
To vent his anger, the Ninth Prince

38
00:02:30,280 --> 00:02:32,240
Will definitely kill all my people

39
00:02:33,160 --> 00:02:34,680
He's just too evil

40
00:02:35,920 --> 00:02:37,400
The Dragon Clan is all like this

41
00:02:38,080 --> 00:02:39,720
The Ninth Prince is especially cruel

42
00:02:40,280 --> 00:02:41,000
I swear

43
00:02:41,000 --> 00:02:42,400
As long as you send me back

44
00:02:42,400 --> 00:02:44,160
I will immediately take my people and flee

45
00:02:44,160 --> 00:02:45,880
We will never be enemies with Chentang Pass again

46
00:03:27,720 --> 00:03:28,760
General Li

47
00:03:28,760 --> 00:03:29,560
Please stop

48
00:03:29,840 --> 00:03:31,240
I have made peace with Miss Yin

49
00:03:35,760 --> 00:03:36,840
How can you prove it?

50
00:03:37,120 --> 00:03:39,440
Miss Yin asked me to give you a message

51
00:03:55,520 --> 00:03:56,720
Tempered by heavenly fire

52
00:03:57,040 --> 00:03:58,120
it becomes soft around the finger

53
00:03:58,400 --> 00:03:59,280
Rise

54
00:04:12,160 --> 00:04:12,680
Sir

55
00:04:12,680 --> 00:04:13,240
Miss

56
00:04:13,440 --> 00:04:14,240
You have great taste

57
00:04:14,360 --> 00:04:16,640
This is our new wedding ring for this season

58
00:04:17,280 --> 00:04:18,520
To hold your hand

59
00:04:18,840 --> 00:04:19,920
And grow old with you

60
00:04:28,720 --> 00:04:29,400
Watch out

61
00:04:29,800 --> 00:04:30,600
Li Jing

62
00:04:52,160 --> 00:04:54,120
Good lord, these two big suitcases

63
00:04:54,120 --> 00:04:56,200
Is our daughter going on a business trip again?

64
00:04:56,520 --> 00:04:57,840
She said she's going to find Li Jing

65
00:04:57,840 --> 00:04:59,320
To help Li Jing fight monsters

66
00:04:59,320 --> 00:05:00,400
Which Li Jing?

67
00:05:00,920 --> 00:05:01,840
Who else?

68
00:05:02,240 --> 00:05:03,520
Nezha's dad
